The paper deals with assessing the quality of 3D printed models, which involves computer graphics (cs.CG) and computer vision (cs.CV) techniques. The use of Topological Data Analysis (TDA) suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-category of geometric reasoning (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper may be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and social and information networks (cs.SI) as it discusses techniques for analyzing and identifying anomalies in data.
